{"lang": "zh_CN", "eventid": "act51side", "eventName": "人们，我们", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "PA-7", "avgTag": "行动前", "storyName": "死结两端", "storyInfo": "通过分销紧缺的能源，弑君者与圣骏堡的工人们建立了联系。为了与能源的供应方保持联络，弑君者决定寻找新的通讯设备，而偶然遇见的古米正好给她提供了线索。", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_towerinside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>圣骏堡，罗德岛临时办事处</><p=2>冬季舞会一周前</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坚雷女士，我来提交近期的报告——", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......坚雷女士？", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "fadeout": "true", "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_heavyobject_putdown", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前只有一片混乱，看不出任何有人的踪迹。弑君者开始把面前的纸箱搬开，试图给自己清出一条道路来。"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎么还是这么乱......完全没地方下脚。", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坚雷——", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "bstart": 0.3, "bend": 0.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是谁在外面？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坚雷教官不在，报告可以给我。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，是你。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坚雷女士呢？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道，我也刚从外面回来没几天，现在办事处里只有我和拉达——就是古米，只有我们俩在。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正式建立办事处的事刚定下来，其他人大概在到处跑手续。我马上也要出去一趟，有份学联的稿件要争取在这几天发出去——", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的报告在这，麻烦你转交一下。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......行。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还有什么事？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虽然你看上去好像不愿意跟我们说话，总是独来独往，但大家都是乌萨斯人，如今又都是罗德岛的干员。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "现在新建办事处，什么都要从头开始，我想，也许我们可以互相帮助，提高点效率。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你们需要什么？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是！我是想说，如果你有什么需要，是可以向办事处、向我们寻求帮助的，懂吗？没必要什么事都自己扛着。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当然，如果我们需要，也会找你的。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教官说你除了定期递交报告之外，和办事处的人没有任何交集，虽然我觉得各司其职也不错，但你刚好来了，我就说一声。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不会希望我频繁出现在这里的。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "别擅自决定我的想法。我知道你和切城，甚至和整合运动有关系，但你到底干了什么，我不知道，也暂时不打算去了解。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对我们来说那是个会反复开裂的伤口，可什么都躲着也不会让它真正长合。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更重要的是，你和我们站在一起，现在又正是缺人的时候，这就够了。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，如果你需要帮助，不要忘了告诉我们。", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1051_headb2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂！", "name": "凛冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "谢谢。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果需要，我会的。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1051_headb2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 1.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "72_g1_sjbstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>圣骏堡，学院滨河街道警察分局</><p=2>12月24日 7:45 A.M.</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉！", "name": "被捕的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我正想去保释你。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就感谢有人做好事，又给咱们省了一笔保释金吧！", "name": "被捕的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是怎么被放出来的？刚才的爆炸声又是......", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——都逃跑——", "name": "远处的声音"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快追——！", "name": "远处的声音"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "圣骏堡嘛，这种事不稀奇。", "name": "被捕的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还是先别说了，要是站这等那些草包警察过来，我就又得进去蹲着了。", "name": "被捕的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......先别回去，跟我走。我还有事要问你。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_oldwarehouse_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎么知道我被条子带走了？我还以为自己要在那蹲坑蹲到天荒地老呢。", "name": "被捕的工人"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人看到你被警察问话，住在你对面的那个小孩，记得吗？", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小孩？红头发的那个？我只记得他看上去阴恻恻的，有点讨人厌——", "name": "被捕的工人"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要以貌取人。你手上的货都卖完了吗？", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还有一个人没跟我碰头，被抓走之前我就是在等他。奥多耶夫区的那个......叫什么来着？", "name": "被捕的工人"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鲁斯，理发师，住在第五大道，他家里有两个刚出生的孩子，妻子死于流感并发症。", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对......对，是他。除了他之外，其他人我都已经交接好了。", "name": "被捕的工人"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能量转换器的钱他们都是怎么付的？", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？不是不用付钱吗？只要持续找我们买货，能量转换器就算送给他们了。", "name": "被捕的工人"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没错。", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......原来你在考我！我有这么不可靠吗？", "name": "被捕的工人"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可靠的人一般不会让自己被抓进拘留所里。", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "别提了，聊事儿，聊事儿！", "name": "被捕的工人"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在担心我或者其他人背着你用能量转换器赚差价吗？", "name": "被捕的工人"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不会的，现在大家都服你了，全靠你，我们才没被冻死，大伙谢谢你还来不及呢——", "name": "被捕的工人"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我理解你们中有的人想多赚些钱的理由，但方法不该是去剥削比自己生活得更困难的人，这不是我选择分销时想看到的。", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有其他渠道，却选择和你们分销而不是独自经营，这样做是徒增风险，你们应该明白。", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "说真的，我到现在都不懂你为什么要做这么吃力不讨好的事......宁愿自己吃亏，也要给其他人提供便利。", "name": "被捕的工人"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鲁斯那边我已经交接好了，但之后招揽新客户的事需要暂停一段时间，有消息我再通知你。", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？那我们这段时间的供应会被断掉吗？", "name": "被捕的工人"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前的储备还能支撑现有用户的需要，大概能维持两周左右，在这期间，我会想办法接上货源。", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果有新客户找上门来，小心辨认，用我给你的那些钱，能帮的话就帮一下，但不要告诉他们供应链的问题，以免引起恐慌。", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我当然是相信你的......有什么我能帮你的吗？", "name": "被捕的工人"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用，这是我的责任。接下来我可能会出城几天，如果有人问起我的动向，你替我应付一下。", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "谢谢。", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这个好说，但如果真有什么事，我该怎么联系你？", "name": "被捕的工人"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还是来这里，给我留封信，像我之前教你们的那样。", "name": "弑君者"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "72_g15_wideunder", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉！好久没在下面看到你了，是要出城去吗？", "name": "热情的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，有点事。前面哪个出口现在没人守着？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都有，不过他们看到是你，肯定不会拦着的。", "name": "热情的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最近没有可疑的人试图从动力层进来，对吧？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没有，警察巡逻得也少了，如果你问的是哪个出口没有警察，答案是一样的。他们只在固定的时间过来，多数时候都是咱们自己看着。", "name": "热情的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，谢谢你。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早点回来啊！", "name": "热情的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1979_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......应该是这儿......", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弑君者蹲下身，抹去地上的积灰，一道用刀锋凿出来的印记逐渐清晰。"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抬头望去，一模一样的应急逃生梯被整齐地安装在各级结构之间。她攀上其中一架逃生梯，来到动力层的更深处。"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_climbmetalladder"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g3_cottage", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能听见吗？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"maskid": "group_interclude_square_common", "char": "？？？", "switch": "true", "style": 1.0, "size": "400, 720", "offset": "300,0", "channel": 3.0, "tsfrom": "0,1", "tsto": "1,1", "tsduration": 0.5}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你那边安全吗？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这是新的安全屋，已经确认过没有窃听器和监控摄像头。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我时间有限......", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你还好吗？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不太好，但这不重要。我们偷偷往圣骏堡转移能源这件事很可能已经被发现了，我暂时还没有受到处罚......", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#6$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他们已经翻新了通讯基站，很可能下一步是新建能源管道，然后将原来的那条废弃。在这之前，我们必须做好两手准备。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你还打算继续在要新建的管道上做手脚？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是打算，而是必须。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原本的管道就已经算得上是萨列夫格勒区特供的了，现在他们大概想把新管道定向铺设至皇宫，连其他的贵族也不管了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "说是为了“节省资源”，可不断新建不知道什么时候就会被天灾摧毁的管道就不是一种浪费了吗？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我听说这边已经有工人被抽调走了，圣骏堡没有任何相关消息吗？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没有，圣骏堡本身......有它的问题。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是指之前提到过的那些学生——", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算矿脉枯竭的消息没能被封锁，你们正在研究的东西还是给了议会拖延的时间。加上第四集团军前不久也面临了自己内部的动乱......", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "贵族、军队、工人，这里暂时都没人轻举妄动，除了对这些背后的暗涌一无所知的学生。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，我不是在指责你。只是，如果你能告诉我更多关于你们正在研究的项目——", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#6$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先说正事吧。在新管道建成之前，原先的那条应该还会继续使用，只是我们的通讯方式必须得更换了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我记得你现在用的通讯装置，连的是外国公司的独立线路？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，租用了乌萨斯境内外资公司的通讯基站。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这就是问题。就算是外资公司，只要基站在乌萨斯境内，就还是可能会受到严密监控，在远北“广播”事件之后更是如此。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每次都更换匿名通讯频道也不行吗？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "现在这边的通讯基站被翻新了，很难说会不会加了什么新功能。你能找到独立搭建线路的无线电通讯设备吗？不经过商用基站的那种？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像是，更精密的、稀有的军用级设备？那可能需要花点时间。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "试试吧，试试。如果你找到了，可以继续用这个频道尝试联络我。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果没有......那恐怕就只能等我找到机会，再主动联络你了。要是两周之后我还没有消息，你就销毁所有和我联络过的痕迹。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我们都先想想办法吧。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保重。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，保重。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "clear": "true", "tsduration": 0.5, "tsfrom": "1,1", "tsto": "0,1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "clear": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G9_rhodes_xqoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>圣骏堡，罗德岛临时办事处</><p=2>冬季舞会数日后</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#21$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的真的不能出去帮忙吗？", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#21$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烈夏姐留下一封信就走了，真理姐她们也没怎么回过办事处，难道她们不需要我的帮助吗？", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#11$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凛冬姐是为了我才被抓走的，可我什么也做不到——", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#15$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古米，我理解你的担忧，但在下一批驻守干员抵达圣骏堡之前，必须有人留在这里，帮忙处理办事处业务。", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#10$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新建感染者收治中心、协助政府进行感染者登记和管理，还有很多事等着我们去做呢。", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#3$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，这些也是让正在外面奔走，或暂时陷入困境的她们，没有后顾之忧的重要任务！", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#7$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这些都很重要，我明白。可如果我唯独在救凛冬姐这件事上帮不上忙......", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#15$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想这样。那天要不是我出了状况，凛冬姐也不会被抓走！", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我理解你的心情，小熊，但我也答应了真理她们要保护——", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#10$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凛冬在吗？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#8$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凛冬姐被警察抓走了——咦，弑君者小姐！", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#9$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......可以直接叫我柳德米拉。你说凛冬被警察抓走了是什么意思？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......该死。我该早几天过来的。你们知道她现在在哪儿吗？我能帮什么忙？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凛冬在封锁区，救她的事我们已经在想办法了。", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#3$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "封锁区？卡托加区？那地方基本已经是巴普洛维奇的独立王国了，你们——罗德岛在这其中能做什么？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#15$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是乌萨斯学生自治团......是这些孩子们，自己在想办法救自己的同伴。", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#10$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我没有帮上忙！凛冬姐是因为我才被抓进去的，我却什么也做不了......", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#15$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你们确定凛冬目前被关在封锁区里？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早露通过多方查证，确认了这点。她也已经通过某种渠道见过那位巴普洛维奇大人。", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#3$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她也没办法把凛冬救出来......或者说，是凛冬自己不想走。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凛冬姐不想出来？", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#11$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你为什么这么说——", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#8$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......直觉。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "办事处有没有更新型号的通讯器？独立搭建线路的那种，不走商用通讯基站。这几天我找了很多渠道，连黑市都没人出售。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这种东西听起来是只有各国军方，或者可露希尔那种喜欢自己瞎鼓捣的家伙才会有的。", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#9$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除非特别申请，不然普通办事处一般都没有这种级别的配置。你要做什么？", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#3$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "救人。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早露说封锁区实行通讯静默，就算有这种通讯器也没用。", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#3$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（低声）不，这是为了联系帮我偷电的人。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和那个人的联络很可能已经被发现了，需要换个更安全的方式。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "偷——", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#2$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "偷电？！", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#9$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘘。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#2$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......最近城里出现的便宜能源，原来是你在运作。", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#2$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还有很多人在帮忙。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，我不该这么惊讶的。你比我们早到乌萨斯，中央区的情报网络也是你搭起来的，能做到这种事也不奇怪。", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#3$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然办事处没有我要的通讯器，那我就先走了。你们保护好自己，凛冬那边我也会想办法的。", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_260_durnar_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也小心，可别被发现了。", "name": "坚雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_260_durnar_1#7$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#21$1"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小声）通讯器......通讯器？", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#21$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什么？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想起来了！", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#9$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们在舞会那天用过的窃听器，就是有个学生自己做的，凛冬姐说她还有一整套自己搭建的无线电通讯设备——", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#11$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这个学生现在在哪儿？", "name": "弑君者"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#4$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_196_sunbr_1#21$1"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不知道。东西是凛冬姐借到的，可能只有她才知道那个人在哪儿了。", "name": "古米"}, "figure_art": "avg_196_sunbr_1#21$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}